Setup

Creating a clean gh-pages branch

# https://gist.github.com/ramnathv/2227408
cd /path/to/repo-name
git symbolic-ref HEAD refs/heads/gh-pages
rm .git/index
git clean -fdx


Gitbook auto commit script

# Run this command under the gitbook folder
cat > gbsync.sh 
bash gbsync.sh
